{"legislative_session": "20252026", "identifier": "AB2700", "title": "Electricity: rate reduction: report.", "from_organization": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": ["bill"], "subject": ["Electricity", "ratereduction", "report"], "abstracts": [{"note": "summary", "abstract": "Existing law vests the Public Utilities Commission with regulatory authority over public utilities, including electrical corporations. Existing law authorizes the commission to fix the rates and charges for every public utility and requires that those rates and charges be just and reasonable.\n\nThis bill would require the commission to generate a report outlining recommendations to decrease the kilowatt-per-hour rate for electricity charged to ratepayers by not less than 30% by January 1, 2028. The bill would require the commission, in making those rate-reduction recommendations, to take certain actions, including to review, and evaluate the cost effectiveness of, certain public purposes programs and to audit electrical corporation wildfire mitigation plan costs, as specified. The bill would require the commission to also include in its report an assessment of verified restitution shortfalls for victims of wildfires caused by electrical corporations occurring before July 12, 2019. The bill would further require the commission to recommend mechanisms for electrical corporations to address those shortfalls, as provided."}], "other_titles": [{"note": "", "title": "Public utilities: rates."}], "other_identifiers": [{"identifier": "ocd-bill-ca-20252026-ab2700"}], "actions": [{"description": "Read first time. To print.", "date": "2026-02-20", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": ["reading-1"], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "From printer. May be heard in committee March 23.", "date": "2026-02-21", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Referred to Com. on U. & E.", "date": "2026-03-09", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": ["referral-committee"], "related_entities": [{"name": "Com. on U. & E.", "entity_type": "organization", "organization_id": null}]}, {"description": "From committee chair, with author's amendments: Amend, and re-refer to Com. on U. & E. Read second time and amended.", "date": "2026-03-10", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": ["amendment-introduction", "amendment-passage", "reading-1", "reading-2"], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Re-referred to Com. on U. & E.", "date": "2026-03-11", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": ["referral-committee"], "related_entities": [{"name": "Com. on U. & E.", "entity_type": "organization", "organization_id": null}]}, {"description": "From committee chair, with author's amendments: Amend, and re-refer to Com. on U. & E. Read second time and amended.", "date": "2026-03-23", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": ["amendment-introduction", "amendment-passage", "reading-1", "reading-2"], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Re-referred to Com. on U. & E.", "date": "2026-03-24", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": ["referral-committee"], "related_entities": [{"name": "Com. on U. & E.", "entity_type": "organization", "organization_id": null}]}, {"description": "Coauthors revised.", "date": "2026-04-09", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "From committee: Do pass and re-refer to Com. on APPR. with recommendation: To Consent Calendar. (Ayes 17. Noes 0.) (April 8). Re-referred to Com. on APPR.", "date": "2026-04-09", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": ["committee-passage", "committee-passage-favorable", "referral-committee"], "related_entities": [{"name": "Com. on AP